title: Week 11 Recap, Bad Quarterback Play, Playoff Picture (Football 11/20)
description:
Will Brinson, Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora recap everything you need to know from Week 11 in the NFL. First, Will and JLC hit on the Nathan Peterman debacle in Buffalo, what to make of the AFC West, Brett Hundley's struggles in Green Bay and the Jaguars being a pretender due to their quarterback play. Nick and Pete join Will to discuss Kirk Cousins, Andy Reid losing!? off the bye, and big picture playoff picture across the league.
